05/slide1-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="474" height="356" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Partnership for Better Health created and approved by Ministry of Interior on 22 October 2012. Partnership for Better Health initiated by at least 100 health professional and expert staff who have great health experiences and legacy works in Cambodia. Our dedicated team of experts and professional staff are committed to enriching quality of health care and social services and better health care system in Cambodia.In collaboration with the Ministry of Health, other Ministries and Health Development Partners, we have developed and implemented a number of innovative and responsive programs and services that promote and support for health care and social services, health care quality and better health system and that also reflect the variety of different lesson learned, experiences, interests and team work cultures.</p>\r\n[/vc_wp_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_empty_space height="15px"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id="sidebar_1"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][dt_fancy_title title="Publications" title_align="left" title_size="h4"][vc_empty_space][dt_blog_masonry layout="gradient_rollover" custom_content_bg_color="rgba(25,25,25,0.47)" post_content_paddings="20px 10px 20px 10px" image_scale_animation_on_hover="n" all_posts_the_same_width="y" dis_posts_total="4" content_alignment="center" post_title_font_style="normal:normal:none" custom_title_color="#ffffff" post_date="n" post_category="n" post_author="n" post_comments="n" custom_meta_color="#ffffff" meta_info_bottom_margin="10px" excerpt_words_limit="10" custom_content_color="#ffffff" read_more_button="off" navigation_font_color="#ffffff" category="6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][dt_fancy_title title="Sponsors and Partners" title_align="left" title_size="h4"][vc_empty_space][ultimate_carousel speed="400"][vc_single_image image="1946" img_size="1