(2089, 1, '2018-06-24 01:29:21', '2018-06-24 01:29:21', 'Kunming city, China\r\n23-25 July 2014Dr. Mean Reatanak Sambath, Executive Director of Partnership for Better Health, attended China Health Information Technology Exchange Conference on 23-25 July 2014 in Kunming city, China. This is a WHO/AeHIN meeting with the participants of Chinese over than 2000 persons. This is a first exchange forum between China and AeHIN. A lots of ehealth are happened in China.\r\n\r\nAeHIN team members visited First Affiliated Hospital of Kunming Medical University. This is a big hospital in Kunming city of China, a busy hospital with about 12000 patients per day.\r\n\r\nAt day 3 of the conference, Dr. Sambath made a presentation of ehealth activities in Cambodia. There are participants from several countries such as Buthan, Cambodia, China (Hong Kong), India, Indonesia, Lao PDR, Malaysia, South Korea, Sri Lanka, Philippine and Thailand.', 'China Health Information Technology Exchange Conference', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2041-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-06-24 01:29:21', '2018-06-24 01:29:21', '', 2041, 'http://localhost/bkpbhcam/2018/06/24/2041-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
